I received a call from Meng Jing.

68
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:49,120
She said the school break in France is almost over.

69
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:56,780
I know. There's only one week left, right?

70
00:10:56,780 --> 00:11:01,490
I've been counting the days.

71
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:04,120
Don't be like this. I'm just going there

72
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,500
to study. I'll be back very soon.

73
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:08,220
You still have one whole semester left.

74
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:10,160
One semester passes by very quickly.

75
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,440
Besides, I can come back to see you when I'm on break.

76
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,350
You can also fly there to see me.

77
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:16,120
Paris is very near.

78
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:19,520
Besides, communication is so convenient nowadays. You can send me

79
