WeChat messages and make video calls.

80
00:11:21,530 --> 00:11:25,890
I promise I'll be there whenever you need me, okay?

81
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:28,790
I just can't bear for you to leave.

82
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:31,290
I can't bear leaving you as well.

83
00:11:33,410 --> 00:11:35,340
Hurry and eat. Weren't you hungry?

84
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:37,620
Then don't be upset.

85
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:50,890
I'm sorry about today.

86
00:11:50,890 --> 00:11:53,480
I was too busy and was not able to spend time with you.

87
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,380
It's fine.

88
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:05,180
What do you think? Does the food suit your taste?

89
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:08,130
It's quite delicious. Is this place new?

90
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:09,250
It's been around for a while.

91
00:12:09,250 --> 00:12:12,070
But they only serve regulars.

92
00:12:12,070 --> 00:12:16,000
You've just come back and you've already found such a nice place to eat.

93
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:20,730
Of course, I have to be prepared for future dates and stuff.

94
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:24,230
Does that mean you've found a girlfriend?

95
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:27,060
I guess so.

96
00:12:27,060 --> 00:12:29,170
It's just that, I don't know if she'll agree or not.

97
00:12:29,170 --> 00:12:31,360
- Then ask her.
- What?

98
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:33,220
Ask her directly?

99
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,750
Of course. The more straightforward, the better.

100
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:38,270
Then, will you be my girlfriend?

101
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:40,260
Yes, just like that.

102
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:48,150
Me?

103
00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:51,330
Will you be my girlfriend?

104
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:57,730
I'm not kidding. I'm serious, Xueling.

105
00:12:58,450 --> 00:13:01,320
Ever since I met you again after coming back,

106
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:05,280
I realize that my feelings for you have never faded.

107
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:09,700
Before, I wasn't confident so I didn't dare express them.

108
00:13:09,700 --> 00:13:13,320
But this time, I don't want to miss the opportunity again.

109
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:16,360
I hope that you give me a chance to stay by your side,

110
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,710
and to take care of you. Will you?

111
00:13:22,940 --> 00:13:26,020
Yan Xu, I can't say yes.

112
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:29,400
Because there's always been someone in my heart.

113
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:35,080
Even though I'm not sure if he and I will end up together,

114
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:39,210
he's been the only one in my heart since I was young.

115
00:13:39,210 --> 00:13:41,010
I'm sorry.

116
00:13:43,830 --> 00:13:45,260
Well...

117
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:47,760
You're not together yet, right?

118
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:50,330
Then I still stand a chance.

119
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:52,870
Right now, I just want to stay beside you,

120
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:55,820
take care of you, and protect you.

121
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:59,720
If you two end up together,

122
00:14:00,770 --> 00:14:02,590
I'll wish you two happiness.

123
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:05,780
But that's not fair to you.

124
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:10,950
Because I'm not sure if I can let go of him completely or not.

125
00:14:10,950 --> 00:14:13,660
I also don't know how much time it will take to do that.

126
00:14:14,890 --> 00:14:16,760
I'm willing to wait.

127
00:14:21,190 --> 00:14:24,790
I forgot you still have to return to France.

128
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:26,330
Didn't I request for leave before?

129
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:28,690
The product launch is over now

130
00:14:28,690 --> 00:14:30,860
so I have to go back to school.

131
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:33,650
Okay, school is important.

132
00:14:33,650 --> 00:14:35,720
Have you told President Tang?

133
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,350
Yes, he knows.

134
00:14:38,350 --> 00:14:40,110
There's not much to do for me.

135
00:14:40,110 --> 00:14:43,020
There's no work for you to turn in either.

136
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:47,670
It's just that, you came back and helped me so much.

137
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:50,190
I feel reluctant to see you go.

138
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:55,100
How about this? Let me organize a send-off party for you.

139
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,600
We can forget about a send-off party. That's too high profile.

140
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:00,550
We all have been occupied with the product launch lately, and never had the time for a gathering.

141
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:03,620
We can use you as an excuse to get together.

142
00:15:05,070 --> 00:15:07,750
All right, let's do as you said. Thank you.

143
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,350
You've helped me so much.

144
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:12,550
I'm the one who should thank you.

145
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:31,340
[Mo Fei: Let's have dinner together.]

146
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:45,890
Hold on. Teacher Cheng,

147
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:47,190
let me make a toast to you.

148
00:15:47,190 --> 00:15:49,630
- Please wait a moment, let me...
- I really want to make a toast to you.

149
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,570
- I, Yu Xia—
- Sit down and speak.

150
00:15:50,570 --> 00:15:53,450
Listen to me. Since I, Yu Xia, came to the company, you have been the one to teach me so much.

151
00:15:53,450 --> 00:15:55,780
I can't drink when you are standing. Sit and drink.

152
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:57,210
Okay, Bro.

153
00:15:57,210 --> 00:15:59,200
Thank you for teaching me so much, Teacher Cheng.

154
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:01,470
Mo Fei, a toast to you.

155
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:03,350
Thank you for teaching...

156
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:06,470
I thank you from the bottom of my heart.

157
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:08,010
Okay.

158
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:11,210
Don't take mine.

159
00:16:13,370 --> 00:16:15,690
You've got to be...

160
00:16:15,690 --> 00:16:19,020
eager to learn.
 [Tang Mingxuan: You clearly know that I can't bear to have you leave]

161
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:22,520
I know. I know that I'm too casual at times.
 [yet you still want me to send-you off.]

162
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,840
You can't be casual.

163
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:28,850
Fashion design is a form of art.

164
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:34,460
Dongdong, I'll toast to you.

165
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:37,330
- I'll toast to you with tripe.
- I don't want that.

166
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:39,370
Take it easy.

167
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:43,870
This isn't cooked yet, bro.

168
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:46,140
It's cooked. I guarantee it's cooked.
[Mo Fei: Cheng Yang thinks, the more, the merrier.]

169
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:49,120
It's definitely cooked. How could it be uncooked after 20 minutes? Should I feed you?

170
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:52,530
Thank you. With those hands of yours, I'll pass.

171
00:16:52,530 --> 00:16:55,220
- A toast to you.
- Hey.

172
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:56,960
Everyone, listen to me.

173
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:02,750
- I think I'm too loud. I'll lower my voice.
- No, no.

174
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:07,570
Today, since President Tang is with us, which is rare,

175
00:17:07,570 --> 00:17:11,220
let's all make a toast to President Tang.

176
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,720
A toast to President Tang.

177
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:15,860
Mo Fei is the one leaving. You should make a toast to her.

178
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:18,110
- A toast to Mo Fei.
- Come on, a toast to Mo Fei.

179
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:23,800
President Tang, join us.

180
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,660
- All right.
- Thank you, President Tang.

181
00:17:25,660 --> 00:17:27,880
Thank you, everyone.

182
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:38,060
So, Mo Fei, shouldn't you say a few words

183
00:17:38,060 --> 00:17:40,360
to President Tang on behalf of all of us?

184
00:17:47,650 --> 00:17:52,110
Thank you, President Tang, for coming to my send-off party.

185
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:53,630
No!

186
00:17:53,630 --> 00:17:55,800
That's too simple. Who wants to hear that?

187
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:58,880
Exactly. You are leaving the country. Say something touching.

188
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:02,360
At least express your sentiments about parting.

189
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:05,690
This isn't really a parting. Since the internet is so developed,

190
00:18:05,690 --> 00:18:08,490
we can see each other at any time. Right?

191
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:11,770
Right?

192
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:16,130
So you'll come to see me often, right?

193
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:22,660
- I will.
- Pinkie promise.

194
00:18:37,670 --> 00:18:40,780
We're such third wheels here.

195
00:18:41,540 --> 00:18:42,830
Cheers.

196
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,020
- Cheers. Thank you, everyone.
- Cheers.

197
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:47,680
- Cheers.
- Let's wish Mo Fei a safe trip.

198
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:50,120
- Thank you.
- You got this.

199
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,910
Today's sales in all the stores

200
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:55,920
are more than double the usual amount. What do you think?

201
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,300
Can we keep up with the replenishment of stocks?

202
00:18:57,300 --> 00:19:00,200
No problem. We've already arranged in advance. Speed isn't a problem.

203
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:04,350
You don't need to do it too quickly. After all, what's scarce is precious.

204
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:07,270
Please thank everyone for their hard work for me.

205
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:09,850
We all worked hard. You did too.

206
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:13,440
When you are working, you look quite formidable and cool.

207
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:15,310
I'm sorry, I forgot.

208
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:19,370
Well, you two chat. I'll get going. Bye-bye.

209
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:21,800
It's fine. Waiting for a short time

210
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:24,880
will only make me more excited to see you.

211
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:28,540
You must have waited for a long time. How about this? Dinner is on me.

212
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:31,080
It's already very late.

213
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:33,980
The restaurant reservation has been canceled.

214
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:36,640
Then, what shall we do?

215
00:19:38,290 --> 00:19:41,260
Originally, I was going to treat you to a fancy meal.

216
00:19:41,260 --> 00:19:44,070
But we ended up eating so simply. I hope you don't mind.

217
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:46,310
I'm the one who should be apologizing.

218
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:49,000
I was so busy that I lost track of the time.

219
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,640
It's fine.

220
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:04,660
Yan Xu, do you have a plan for the future?

221
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:13,120
My biggest wish is that when I grow old,

222
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:15,600
I can be with my beloved one

223
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,690
and be far away from the bustling city,

224
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:21,160
spending the rest of our lives by the sea.

225
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:27,130
Leaving everything behind, and going back to the basics

226
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:30,240
is indeed a life that one would look forward to.

227
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:39,950
Xueling, are you willing to do that with me?

228
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:46,350
I haven't made up my mind about the future yet.

229
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:51,280
That's fine.

230
00:20:52,090 --> 00:20:54,850
We still have time to waste.

231
00:20:54,850 --> 00:20:58,140
Besides, you being able to be with me here today,

232
00:20:58,140 --> 00:21:01,070
I feel like half of my wish has already come true.

233
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:11,800
If we really lived by the ocean,

234
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:15,400
aside from the moonlight, there should be a sky filled with stars. Right?

235
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:19,900
It's such a shame, that we live in the city.

236
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:23,600
The lights are too bright. You can't see anything.

237
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:27,660
Leave it to me.

238
00:21:30,770 --> 00:21:32,830
When did you prepare that?

239
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:39,300
We played with these together when we were at school, do you remember?

240
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:49,600
It's really been so long since I've played with these.

241
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,600
Stars.

242
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:11,200
Based on this,

243
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:15,000
