244
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:17,800
And a lot of large orders are coming in.

245
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:20,600
Institutions are probably optimistic about our Mingyuan Group.

246
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:23,000
Stock markets are all about people buying and selling, right?

247
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:25,200
Buying Mingyuan's stocks can earn money.

248
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,800
That's right.

249
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:28,800
After our show,

250
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:31,400
the feedback from malls and online platforms are both good.

251
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:35,800
