252
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,400
Exactly.

253
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:41,600
You're worried when the prices go up and you're worried when the prices don't.

254
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:43,000
You'll get sick this way.

255
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:46,000
Okay, all right. I'll stop looking at it.

256
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:48,600
Old Xia and I are meeting for golf today.

257
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:51,200
Do you have time? Let's go together.

258
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:55,200
I won't join you, Dad. There is a lot to do at the company today.

259
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,200
All right.

260
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:59,400
You must maintain a good relationship with Uncle Xia.

261
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:04,100
Speaking of, Xueling hasn't been here for a meal in a long time now.

262
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:08,400
What?

263
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,400
Did you choke?

264
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:14,800
The child already said he's busy with work and doesn't have time.

265
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:18,800
Let him handle his own affairs. Stop worrying for him.

266
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:21,400
I'm his mom. Can I not worry?

267
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:24,400
In this world, is there a mom who doesn't worry about her child's marriage?

268
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:27,000
Should I be like you, and not care, ask, nor listen?

269
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:30,300
He said he has a girlfriend already.

270
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:33,000
- Did I acknowledge her?
- Mom.

271
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:34,800
Do you want me to marry two women?

272
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:37,400
Right. Do you agree to that?

273
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:40,800
You two.

274
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:43,000
Do you dare?

275
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,600
Enjoy your meal. I'm going to work.

276
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:46,800
You haven't finished your bun yet.

277
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:48,800
I won't eat that, Dad. I'm full.

278
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,200
Bye-bye, Mom.

279
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,600
You little brat.

280
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:55,900
He only ate half of his breakfast. It's all because of you.

281
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:58,930
What do you mean?

282
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,500
Bring me my medicine.

283
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:13,770
President Fang.

284
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:17,000
Are you feeling unwell, President Fang?

285
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:19,090
No.

286
00:24:19,090 --> 00:24:21,930
I'm just a little dizzy.

287
00:24:21,930 --> 00:24:23,300
What is it?

288
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:26,500
I've been working on buying the stocks per your instructions.

289
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:30,600
- How much were you able to buy?
- Almost three percent.

290
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:33,400
Three percent.

291
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:36,200
All right, I got it.

292
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:38,200
Continue buying.

293
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:39,800
Okay.

294
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:41,850
Don't be too obvious.

295
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:45,300
I understand.

296
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:49,200
What? We only sold five items today?

297
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:51,400
In addition, 57 were returned or exchanged.

298
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:56,200
There are also comments saying that our clothing's quality is not as good as Mingyuan's.

299
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:58,400
That's such bullshit.

300
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,230
Do they have mouths to just eat?

301
00:25:00,230 --> 00:25:02,800
When it's time to speak, why are they keeping their mouth shut?

302
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:05,800
They can't even handle sales returns and exchanges. What's the use of keeping them?

303
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:07,800
They are good-for-nothings!

304
00:25:09,600 --> 00:25:10,800
Haitian.

305
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:13,900
Liu Rui, you may leave first.

306
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:18,800
Haitian, why are you here?

307
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:22,600
Aren't you busy with the game?

308
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:26,000
It's a good thing I came.

309
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:30,400
If I hadn't come, I wouldn't have known what was happening to the company.

310
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:37,400
Why have the company's sales fallen so drastically?

311
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:41,300
As the general manager, explain it to me.

312
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:45,600
Haitian, don't be angry first.

313
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:48,600
I don't want this to happen either.

314
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:51,800
Mingyuan's new products have had a big impact on us.

315
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:56,600
So it's normal that our sales declined. After all, they just launched their new products.

316
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:58,400
Don't panic yet.

317
00:25:58,400 --> 00:26:02,000
Don't panic? How do I not panic?

318
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:04,300
That's not the problem at all.

319
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:08,000
Six out of ten things sold have issues.

320
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:11,500
Why? Why would that happen?

321
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:14,400
Let me ask you another thing.

322
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:18,000
Regarding the money, we invested to produce this batch of clothing,

323
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:21,400
where did it go? What did you use it for?

324
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:26,200
What else can I use it for? You've seen the contracts.

325
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:31,100
I used all the money on Haitian Color.

326
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:34,000
If there's a problem with the quality,

327
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,400
it must be the purchasing department's fault.

328
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:38,400
What a load of nonsense!

329
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,630
That's impossible.

330
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:43,000
Old Chen in the purchasing department has been with us for so many years.

331
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:46,600
He's an old employee! I completely trust him!

332
00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:51,400
Don't throw others under the bus when a problem occurs.

333
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:55,600
Haitian, are you suspecting me?

334
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:57,600
I've put sweat and blood into Haiyao as well.

335
00:26:57,600 --> 00:27:00,300
For such a long time, what haven't I done for

336
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:02,600
your and Haiyao's sake?

337
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:14,400
Bai Xiaoman, there better not be a problem with your doings.

338
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:32,600
Is there anything happening with Haiyao recently?

339
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:35,150
I heard that because of their clothing quality,

340
00:27:35,150 --> 00:27:37,600
they have been busy and hard-pressed.

341
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:43,600
This is the best opportunity for us.

342
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:45,800
What do you mean by that?

343
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:48,400
It's time to settle matters with them.

344
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:52,400
Come in.

345
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:57,000
Brother Xuan, this is the draft from the lawyers you asked me to contact. It's ready.

346
00:27:57,960 --> 00:28:00,040
I'll get back to work now.

347
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:13,000
Xueling, take a look.

348
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:22,400
[Yan Xu]

349
00:28:26,150 --> 00:28:28,400
If you need to go do something, go ahead.

350
00:28:29,610 --> 00:28:31,790
It's nothing important.

351
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:38,200
Aside from work, your personal life is very important, too.

352
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,800
Go.

353
00:28:57,700 --> 00:29:01,600
Uncle Fang, you have already acquired five percent of Mingyuan's stocks.

354
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:04,800
You're already considered one of our shareholders.

355
00:29:04,800 --> 00:29:10,200
I am very interested to know why you want to acquire our stocks.

356
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:15,210
I'm a businessman.

357
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:20,800
Before doing anything, I evaluate things from the perspective of profits.

358
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:23,900
After evaluation of pros and cons,

359
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:27,600
do I need to send you a message via WeChat?

360
00:29:32,100 --> 00:29:34,000
To be honest...

361
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:38,000
Well, in the past,

362
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:40,700
Mingyuan experienced lots of crises.

363
00:29:41,810 --> 00:29:44,030
However, it has

364
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:47,110
remained invincible in the industry.

365
00:29:48,100 --> 00:29:52,600
That proves it has value as a brand.

366
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:57,200
The value of a brand is infinite.

367
00:29:57,200 --> 00:30:00,600
And I'm the type who likes to collect things of value.

368
00:30:00,600 --> 00:30:05,200
So, my next plan is to acquire Mingyuan.

369
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:09,000
Acquire Mingyuan?

370
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,500
It won't be that easy.

371
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:16,200
In the past, I've always thought

372
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:20,400
that if the Tang and Xia families became in-laws, the combined stocks

373
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:24,000
might be more than one-third.

374
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:27,600
It would be impossible for me to acquire it. But with the current situation,

375
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:31,800
Mingyuan's stocks are being dispersed all over the place out there.

376
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:35,800
In addition, the Tang and Xia families

377
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:42,000
wouldn't possibly stand on the same side to go against me. Right?

378
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:46,400
So, it's very possible for me to become Mingyuan's biggest shareholder.

379
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:51,200
Uncle Fang, how are you so sure that the Xia family wouldn't do that?

380
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:54,600
The rumors should be true, right?

381
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:57,100
Perhaps they are fake.

382
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,600
It should be true.

383
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:04,400
As the one managing Mingyuan,

384
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:08,300
our Tang family will not give up on Mingyuan.

385
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:14,190
I like your confidence.

386
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:17,400
But remember this, confidence

387
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:21,600
doesn't represent actual capability.

388
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:24,400
- Thank you for the lesson.
- All right.

389
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:36,000
What are we going to do?

390
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:38,410
Mingyuan didn't take any actions against us before

391
00:31:38,410 --> 00:31:40,800
because of their product launch.

392
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:45,000
The point is they have evidence of us stealing the designs.

393
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:47,600
It's over. We are doomed now.

394
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:50,800
Stop pacing back and forth in front of me. It's making me dizzy! How do I come up with a way out of this like that?

395
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:52,200
Bai Xiaoman!

396
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,600
Haitian.

397
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:55,810
I was so blind

398
00:31:55,810 --> 00:31:58,800
to have you help me manage the company.

399
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:02,000
You really are unable to accomplish anything, but good at making everything worse.

400
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:04,600
Since you started managing the company,

401
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:08,400
how many lousy ideas have you come up with?

402
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,600
Don't you know your own capability?

403
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:15,200
You insist on competing with Mingyuan.

404
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:18,000
Take a look at yourself in the mirror!

405
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:20,800
Are you qualified? You stop right there!

406
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:24,500
Shen Jiaxi, you're also a good-for-nothing. I will talk to you in a bit.

407
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:30,290
The issues with return and exchange,

408
00:32:30,290 --> 00:32:33,930
you begged me to give you time to handle it. Fine, I gave you time. Did you resolve it?

409
00:32:33,930 --> 00:32:35,970
You resolved nothing!

410
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:39,890
Now Mingyuan, Tang Mingxuan,

411
00:32:39,890 --> 00:32:42,460
is suing Haiyao.

412
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:45,320
Is this the result of your resolution?

413
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:48,890
Why did you screw Haiyao? Why did you screw me?

414
00:32:50,420 --> 00:32:54,630
Haitian, I-I never did anything to betray you.

415
00:32:54,630 --> 00:32:56,320
Since the day we became a couple...

416
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:59,270
I've focused all my attention on you and the company.

417
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,900
You can't treat me this way.

418
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:02,810
Are you still putting on an act?

419
00:33:02,810 --> 00:33:05,040
You're still putting on an act!

420
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:08,210
Let me ask you one thing.

421
00:33:08,210 --> 00:33:10,150
Why did you hide the fact

422
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:12,240
that you stole the designs from Mingyuan?

423
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,330
Who made you so bold? Who?

424
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:19,560
Stole? What do you mean stole the designs?

425
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:23,610
Jiaxi, how could you steal the designs?

426
00:33:23,610 --> 00:33:25,240
I really didn't know you stole them.

427
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:27,460
I bought them from her!

428
00:33:27,460 --> 00:33:30,000
- Jiaxi, you shouldn't have done something like that.
- Bai Xiaoman!

429
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:32,570
- What are you saying? You clearly—
- Jiaxi.

430
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:35,980
I know you hate Mo Fei. I also know you hate that you couldn't showcase your talent at Mingyuan.

431
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:38,300
But how could you steal the designs?

432
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:41,840
As a friend, I've always wanted to protect you. But this time, I can't do it anymore.

433
00:33:41,840 --> 00:33:45,380
Look at Haitian. If I don't explain things clearly, he won't forgive me.

434
00:33:45,380 --> 00:33:47,620
Bai Xiaoman! Can you act like a human being for once?

435
00:33:47,620 --> 00:33:49,240
You were the one who told me to steal the designs!

436
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:51,290
Enough with the both of you!

437
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,880
Are you still putting on an act here?

438
00:33:58,610 --> 00:34:00,640
Singing a duet?

439
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:04,390
Bai Xiaoman,

440
00:34:04,390 --> 00:34:08,520
I see your true colors clearly now.

441
00:34:09,310 --> 00:34:13,260
If this matter gets resolved, fine.

442
00:34:13,260 --> 00:34:15,610
If it can't be resolved,

443
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:19,340
you both just wait.

444
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:21,550
You two won't get out of this.

445
00:34:29,290 --> 00:34:32,380
Bai Xiaoman, I was so blind.

446
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:34,790
I actually believed what you said.

447
00:34:34,790 --> 00:34:36,730
I don't know if you're blind or not.

448
00:34:36,730 --> 00:34:40,630
However, whether it's in front of Zhu Haitian or the judge, that is what I will say.

449
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:42,780
If I were you, I would have run away long ago.

450
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:45,720
Will I still be here speaking nonsense and waiting for the police to come and arrest me?

451
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:04,610
- Xueling.
- Mom.

452
00:35:04,610 --> 00:35:06,960
Did you just get home? Did you eat yet?

453
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,720
I ate at my friend's place.

454
00:35:08,720 --> 00:35:10,330
A friend's place?

455
00:35:10,330 --> 00:35:12,590
You usually never eat at other people's places.

456
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:15,410
It is a classmate from college.

457
00:35:15,410 --> 00:35:16,850
We haven't been in touch for a long time.

458
00:35:16,850 --> 00:35:20,690
I bumped into the person when they came back to the country to hold an art exhibit.

459
00:35:20,690 --> 00:35:22,960
Is your classmate a girl or a boy?

460
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:25,250
Mom, what do you mean?

461
00:35:25,250 --> 00:35:28,360
Nothing. I'm just asking.

462
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:31,400
It seems like your dad wants to see you.

463
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,560
Tonight, he asked why you haven't come back yet.

464
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:35,720
He's waiting for you downstairs. Go quickly.

465
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:38,620
- All right. I'll go see him.
- Okay.

466
00:35:44,680 --> 00:35:46,840
- Dad, you wanted to see me?
- Yes.

467
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:53,730
What do you think about Fang Weiguo's acquisition of Mingyuan stocks this time?

468
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,410
What do you mean?

469
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:03,010
I think that Uncle Fang is a bit out of line.

470
00:36:03,010 --> 00:36:04,920
Although we say business is business,

471
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:08,260
what he's doing now is taking advantage of the situation.

472
00:36:08,260 --> 00:36:11,020
I don't like this kind of competition.

473
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:14,020
Then, are you supporting the Tang family?

474
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:15,900
Of course, what else?

475
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:18,680
I just wanted to know your opinion.

476
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:23,650
Dad, I don't understand what you mean.

477
00:36:23,650 --> 00:36:27,690
If we don't support our own people now, what will happen to Mingyuan?

478
00:36:28,540 --> 00:36:32,820
Child, that's the reason why I wanted to talk to you today.

479
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:36,910
Actually, regardless of who manages Mingyuan,

480
00:36:36,910 --> 00:36:41,530
it won't affect our family. It might even be a good thing.

481
00:36:41,530 --> 00:36:45,810
Dad, are you having other intentions?

482
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:49,380
If you act this way too, what will Mingxuan do?

483
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,490
It seems like, compared to Mingyuan's future,

484
00:36:52,490 --> 00:36:54,990
you care more about that brat.

485
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:01,900
Let me tell you.

486
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:04,460
No matter who manages the company,

487
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:07,980
we'll either be the second or third-largest shareholder.

488
00:37:07,980 --> 00:37:12,230
When the time comes, they'll be competing to collaborate with us.

489
00:37:22,370 --> 00:37:24,020
[Yan Xu]

490
00:37:25,610 --> 00:37:27,210
Hello.

491
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:30,480
I'm home already. Don't worry.

492
00:37:31,850 --> 00:37:34,760
I have some things to do so I'll call you back later.

493
00:37:37,970 --> 00:37:39,850
Is it Mingxuan?

494
00:37:41,090 --> 00:37:42,640
No, it's not.

495
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:45,760
Then, who is it?

496
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:48,200
Don't ask.

497
00:37:49,170 --> 00:37:53,340
Okay, okay, all right. I won't ask. What is your relationship with Mingxuan now?

498
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:56,380
- What are you referring to?
- You know what I'm referring to.

499
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:58,510
I don't know.

500
00:37:59,810 --> 00:38:02,040
Outside of work.

501
00:38:03,940 --> 00:38:05,610
There's nothing.

502
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,380
Not even a bit?

503
00:38:12,930 --> 00:38:16,510
Perhaps we are not fated for that.

504
00:38:19,890 --> 00:38:22,460
Fate or no fate.

505
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,600
In my opinion,

506
00:38:25,210 --> 00:38:27,490
human effort is the decisive factor, understand?

507
00:38:41,390 --> 00:38:44,260
Child, in life,

508
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:46,160
you will be faced with a lot of choices.

